{"tid":1977184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"戴耀廷：未察知大勢的人，包括法官們　最終會被時代所唾棄","createTime":"2020-04-17T18:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T10:37:08.000Z","uid":171273,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"323516aa18427ad2bf253a44ccefe88e75ab6837","tid":1977184,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:50:39.000Z","msg":"法官在刑事案件中，當然不可以按民意去判一個人有罪與無罪。<br />\n<br />\n但在憲法爭議中，空泛的憲法條文及憲法原則，應如何解釋及引用，卻不能脫離人民對憲制的期望。<br />\n<br />\n法學家H. L. A. Hart 非常經典的學說指出，法律之為法律，是因為受法律規管的人民承認那些是具規範性的規則。換句話說，若人民不再承認一些法律具規範作用，那些法律也會失卻了法律的果效。<br />\n<br />\n憲法學者 Bruce Ackerman 提出憲政時刻（constitutional moment）的說法，指在關鍵時刻，當人民覺得現有憲制或法律未能滿足他們的期望，他們會聯合起來，以憲制和法制以內及以外的所有方法，推動憲制的改變，導致落後於人民思想的立法及司法機關，最終都得改變他們的立場，確立人民所期望的憲制及法律改革。<br />\n<br />\n可以說，香港正處於此憲政時刻。由「佔中」至「反送中」，香港人對法律及憲制的期望，對權力制約及權利保障的渴求，已是現行由當權者所操控的憲制及法制所未能承托。香港人必會繼續用憲制和法制以內及以外的所有方法，去推動香港憲制及法制的轉化。<br />\n<br />\n未能察知這大勢的人，包括了法官們，最終也會被時代所唾棄。"},{"pid":"a6c7f88e56f1563daf030cbc83d5fad9791a13f0","tid":1977184,"uid":251732,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:53:10.000Z","msg":"跟唔上時代變革嘅井底之蛙遲早都會成為餐桌上嘅佳餚"},{"pid":"fb9176012ecb3739d0d8205be61af270f8aa8fa5","tid":1977184,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:26:32.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6883d051f11879357a076dbd193ed9175e3bde9","tid":1977184,"uid":134474,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1jUTEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1jUTEL.jpg&h=5a2c8ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5t3OdEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5t3OdEM.jpg&h=d810b4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今時今日班law友，法官眼中理所當然法治精神其實係革命流血爭取"},{"pid":"5e623e83c732203286b7c63d933847150df76aad","tid":1977184,"uid":2438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:34:13.000Z","msg":"「未能察知這大勢的人，包括了法官們，最終也會被時代所唾棄。」<br />\n<br />\nIronic?"},{"pid":"3151a884d10432e39cc087710dea1281f110b0ee","tid":1977184,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"下一步係把司法迫害定為反人類罪行<br />\n司法迫害行為上等同支持警員強姦同水刑<br />\n<br />\n呢一步可以第227章《裁判官條例》 對法庭的保護撤銷"},{"pid":"cb98fc8d74b1d3bdad5b428c716058bd4751a87d","tid":1977184,"uid":133183,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:37:34.000Z","msg":"晨早已經講，法律如果保護唔到人民，人民根本唔需要遵守。"},{"pid":"ba7562a180880a0314a24b3c2f44466b244b543a","tid":1977184,"uid":215755,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/omP0kt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FomP0kt.gif&h=8e75d16c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4916c0106a040c2535ea117564131f9469c999a0","tid":1977184,"uid":40804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:49:34.000Z","msg":"戴教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望泛民其他人都可以行佢條進化路線"},{"pid":"0a9bea826dbaa48863b1ca67ac7de008261d8345","tid":1977184,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:54:15.000Z","msg":"good point"},{"pid":"5285a1bb52a196adbbbd140007b6a53c6bb1eb5d","tid":1977184,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:55:05.000Z","msg":"正如香港法官當日屈到基本法的游行示威自由非絕對, 可由狗方加門檻限制<br />\n<br />\n點解裁判官條例的寬容會勁到允許裁判官迫害警暴受害人, 會可以容許法院成為反人類罪行共犯<br />\n<br />\n<ins>所以點解一定要咬實強姦案, 因為可以破香港紅官的自以為免死金牌</ins><br />\n<br />\n所有野去到反人類罪就多好多條路"},{"pid":"308310d27387313ea727179391f9306b243ee218","tid":1977184,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:06:44.000Z","msg":"時代革命！到時你就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">香 港 國 寶 ： 許冠傑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973620</a></div>"},{"pid":"559660f4e3521561364308512dd6ce69dcf573bb","tid":1977184,"uid":281328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:20:53.000Z","msg":"當人民覺得現有憲制或法律未能滿足他們的期望，他們會聯合起來<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">以憲制和法制以內及以外的所有方法，推動憲制的改變</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>即係包括:<br />\n街頭勇武抗爭、議會體制內抗爭</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>和勇不分</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4c21a5d781015a64cd4f6e781cdfdc56d4451009","tid":1977184,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7562a180880a0314a24b3c2f44466b244b543a","tid":1977184,"uid":215755,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/omP0kt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FomP0kt.gif&h=8e75d16c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7b500c1011be9c24e2984cddef319a14a2eaaa","tid":1977184,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T22:47:13.000Z","msg":"準備assemble"},{"pid":"300369517c922e5999c49cbcc13af2ee346bd082","tid":1977184,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6883d051f11879357a076dbd193ed9175e3bde9","tid":1977184,"uid":134474,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1jUTEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=